dcterms:description: LiveStream-400 is a weighted undirected graph with 386 viewers/nodes and 61,125 connections/edges in total. The dataset consists of 12 graph snapshots, collected every 5 minutes during the video streaming event.
dcterms:title: LiveStream-400

dcterms:description: LiveStream-20K was generated based on an unmodified video distribution software and consists of 20,357 viewers/nodes and 812,810 connections/edges in total over 12 graph snapshots.
dcterms:title: LiveStream-20K
